 * 16 - 80: cumulative id (64 bits)
 * 80 - 144: cumulative volatility accumulator (64 bits)
 * 144 - 208: cumulative bin crossed (64 bits)
 * 208 - 216: sample lifetime (8 bits)
 * 216 - 256: sample creation timestamp (40 bits)
